name: Doge
description:
A Loving Shiba and Battle Cat's rival.
Trying to enter college this year.
Very thoughtful and sends
birthday gifts to Cat every year.

name: Snache
description:
Uses watercolours for body paint.
So... naturally weak against water.
This information has nothing to do
with the game content whatsoever.

name: Those Guys
description:
A bunch of wusses who like to gang up.
Found each other on the internet.
Surprisingly,
all of them are quite rich.

name: Hippoe
description:
This dangerous hippo has
confidence in its stamina and power.
(S)he? has a multi attack skill.
We don't know if it is a he or a she.

name: Jackie Peng
description:
Loves watching Kung Fu movies,
and aiming to get into Hollywood.
Uses self-taught Kung Fu.

name: Gory
description:
Managed to get kicked out of the zoo
because of his scary face.
Has no job or education,
so turned to alcohol and gambling.

name: Baa Baa
description:
Corny name. Corny looks.
Has a complex about being too ordinary.
Trying to fix this by taking comedy lessons
at acting school.

name: Le'boin
description:
Has ridiculously long reach.
Likes his women curvy. Very curvy.
Collects lots of magazines... don't ask what type.

name: Kang Roo
description:
Always dreamed to be a boxer. 
Couldn't really get there because it is... well, a kangaroo.
Sad, sad truth.

name: Teacher Bear
description: A kindergarten teacher. He LOVES children. His sharp claws are not suited for the job. Not related to a certain other bear. No one knows his real name.

name: Croco
description:
He was saved by Dundee.
Infatuated with correspondence learning.
Managed to obtain several qualifications.
Word Processing Cert. 2nd class.

name: Squire Rel
description:
She speaks an old English dialect (?)
No, seriously, it sounds like English, but it's too hard to understand what she says.
Works at the English school near the station.

name: Ms. Sign
description:
Her family structure is father, mother, brother and a "daddy".
Wants to marry out ASAP. She comes out when you take too long.

name: Master A.
description: Knows all the dirty stuff. His friends from middle school admire him and call him master. Dating experience: zero.

name: R. Ost
description: Stressed about recent hair loss. Yes, his last name is actually Ost. His first name is Rich. Can critical sometimes.

name: Otta-smack-u
description: Earned the nickname by ganging up on their target with a literal smackdown. Holds the keepsake of their ancestors "Just a Normal Rock"

name: Kory
description: A really eccentric koala. He was kicked out from zoo because of food bills so is freeloading at Gory's house. Gory is going to kick him out soon too.
special_ability:
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to the Cat Base);
100% chance to create Lv.4 Shockwaves.

special_ability: Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to the Cat Base).

name: Duche

Talked smack about his friends on
his personal blog, "Just Bein' Honest".
Got too popular and now no one calls
him anymore - the internet never forgets!

Loves going to the tanning salon,
that's why her skin is red.
Born in an organic free range farm.
Did you know that pigs like to clean?

name: Sir Seal

Came to the big city from
the quiet seaside.
Wanted more attention so
dyed his body red.

name: B.B.Bunny

name: Shy Boy

name: Ginger Snache

description: Finally got the zipper on his costume unstuck, now he is free and unstoppable! Can't control the destructive urges that compel him to wreak havoc on everything around him!

name: Mecha-Bun
description: Artifact of an ancient empire which once ruled the Earth. A dark union of Doges has revived this terrible force, but thankfully they only have one copy of the pilot's manual to share!

name: Filibuster Obstructa (Alien/Floating)
description: After millennia lost among the stars, a strange force once again wreaks havoc on the Galactic Cat Empire. The chaos it wields may rewrite the laws of reality...
special_ability:
Long Distance (Effective Range: 300~4,300);
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow and Weaken.

name: Assassin Bear
description: Licensed to kill. The global financial crisis isn't helping him much though. Please check the flyers. He's offering one million per kill now.

name: Doge Dark
description:
One day Doge picked up a flyer and found work as a part time killer.
Works hard everyday to make
money to get into prep school.

name: Gory Black
description: Gory finally found a job! Leaving behind his old life, he is looking forward to seeing his family again when they move back in.

name: Shadow Boxer K (Black)
description:
"You are already dead" - S.B.K
Spits out cheesy lines all the time. Kind of feel sorry for the joey in the pouch that always has put up with it.

name: Director Kurosawah (Black)
description: A washed up director known for copying the very famous movie director. His works are all flops but he is famous for his raunchy scenes.

name: Dark Otter
description: Bears his family's ultimate weapon: "Normal Rock", bane of clams everywhere. It's actually a plum pit, but don't mention it or he'll fly off the handle.

name: Le'noir
description: This ink-black pachy is a manic collector of rare "gentlemen's cinema". Afraid his hobby might be found so smashes anyone who gets near his stash.

name: Tackey
description: A ruthless semi-pro pitcher who resorts to any means necessary to win the game. Throws non-regulation balls from long distance to intimidate the away team batters.

name: Razorback
description: After years of wandering the wastelands, his fur and his soul have been blackened by the corruption of the world. Receives awards for perfect attendance at work.
special_ability: Attack power increases by 50% when under 50% health.

name: Ragin' Gory
description:
Corporate warrior sworn to an evil
multinational. His eyes are bloodshot after
days of overtime, and seeing the new guy
leave after 5PM has driven him berserk.

name: Gory Groom
special_ability: Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base).

name: Selena
special_ability:
100% chance to knockback all Cat Units;
40% chance to slow Cat Units for 200f 6.67 seconds.

name: Bakoo
description: A dream-eating cutie who wanders around half-awake. Still wears a diaper, even though she's fourteen. Don't startle this gentle sleepwalker no matter how loud she snores.
special_ability:
100% chance to freeze all Cat Units for 150f 5 seconds;
Long Distance (Effective Range: 50~1,850).

name: Le'Grim
special_ability: 100% chance to slow all Cat Units for 200f (6.67 seconds).

name: Akuma
special_ability: Multi-hit attack (18,000 at 23f, 18,000 at 27f, 18,000 at 31f);Omni Strike (Effective Range: -450~550)

name: Heavenly Hippoe
description: A Hippoe who yearned for a halo. Styled his hair into wings... which makes him the next best thing to a Pegasus. Amirite?

name: Gabriel
description: Great-grandaddy of the Doge clan. Watches to make sure his descendants keep up their studies: sleeping in class earns a bite from the old man!

name: Angelic Gory
description: An ugly mug is what got this guy chased out of heaven. An old-school fallen angel who makes a living by lurking at the slot machines.

name: Sunfish Jones
description: A Sunfish named Jones. Yeah, so what? Shaped like an [sic] stealth bomber, and therefore undetectable by radar systems. Actually, that's how he got into heaven.
special_ability: 30% chance to slow all Cat Units for 90f 3 seconds.

name: Angelic Sleipnir
description: The eight-legged god-horse of Norse myth. Has to spend most of his paycheck on footwear, so usually spends his weekends staying in and gardening.
special_ability: 15% chance to knockback all Cat Units.

name: Chickful A (Angel)
description: A bright-eyed rookie only on her second day of her heavenly job. Her friend Duche is getting real sick of hearing her go on about how great her new flat in paradise is.
special_ability: 25% chance to freeze all Cat Units for 60f 2 seconds.

name: Mr. Angel
description: Drives everyone around him crazy with self-righteous advice. Best pretend you're listening, or he'll smack you good: "You'll thank me for this someday!"
special_ability: 30% chance to weaken all Cat Units by 50% for 150f 5 seconds.

name: Boraphim (Angel)
description: Executive assistant to heaven's most famous recort [sic] label producer. Ghost-writer for two one-hit wonders: "Cats Ain't No Sin" and "C.P.U. (Future Intelligence Pt. II)"

name: Cala Maria (Angel)
description: A heavenly taste of the sea, sent as a religious vision by the Cat God to those pure of heart. Culinary paradise awaits those who pass this test of faith.

name: Winged Pigge
description: A lovely Pigge with a cute heart-shaped nose. She doesn't mean any harm with her merry bouncing, but it'll crush your will to fight. Just wants to go home to her heavenly family.
special_ability:
100% chance to weaken all Cat Units to 10% for 150f 5 seconds;
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -340~340)

name: Youcan (Angel/Alien)
description: An extra-confident bird named by his parents who wanted him to always believe in himself. His arrogance is so extreme that it consumed his home dimension and drove him to this one.
special_ability:
100% chance to create Lv.3 Shockwaves;
Barrier (Limit: 266,000).

name: St. Dober
description:
Loyal to the end, he waits patiently by the
gates of heaven for his master to arrive.
A famous statue of him in mid-Surge Attack
is a well-known meeting spot for teenagers.
special_ability:
30% chance to create Lv.3 Surge Attacks within a range of 150~350;
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -300~200).

name: Divine Cyclone
description: A wrathful being who cleanses evil with the force of a typhoon. Take care: Angels won’t be harmed by anti-Floating attacks!

name: Cruel Angel Clionel (Angel)
description: This mystical being is humanity's salvation... or it's destruction. But for now, it's too busy being an overprotective single parent who protects its kid with ultra long range attacks.
special_ability:
30% chance to slow Cat Units for 120f 4 seconds;
Long Distance (Effective Range: 400~1,200)

name: Sluggy (Angel)
special_ability: 30% chance to slow Cat Units for 120f 4 seconds.

name: Le'saint
special_ability: Attack power increases by 100% at 50% health

name: Heavenly Herald Papuu
description: Her Archangel qualifying exams are comingup, so she takes her textbooks everywhere.Any Cats who interrupt her studies will bepunished with her Toxic magics. Shhhh!

name: Head Rococo
special_ability:
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -350~425);
100% chance to freeze Cat Units for 120f 4 seconds.

name: Shaman Khan
special_ability:
Knocks back Cat Units (100%)
Long Distance (Effective range: 300~800)

name: Shibalien (Alien)
description: A lovable Doge, genetically modified by the invaders to be the perfect foot soldier! Always says "We think", but is really selfish. That's why he fights with his dorm-mates.

name: Kroxo
description: Overcame his eye condition to get a degree in interior design. His philosophy is "Simple is Best"; turns out he just paints it all blue and takes the rest of the week off.

name: Hyppoh (Alien)
description: This hippoe is a monthly alien abductee. Traumatized by the thing growing from her head, her skin turned as blue as her heart and she had to change her name.

name: Imperator Sael (Alien)
description: A walrus warlord who came from space to fight Earth's Red Seals. No hands, but still tries for handshakes to be polite. Won't see me lyin' about this classy gent.
special_ability: 20% chance to slow Cat Units for 60f 2 seconds.

name: LeMurr (Alien)
description: Her eyes are big enough to see for two lightyears. Daytime is too bright, though, so has to stay inside until dusk. Wears special contacts that reduce Cat Units' Atk.
special_ability: 25% chance to weaken all Cat Units to 20% for 300f 10 seconds.

name: Helmut Krabbe (Alien)
description: Took out a 45-year loan on a durable home to cover up the THAT growing from his rear. Still spends every weekend at open houses. Can survive one lethal strike.
special_ability: 100% chance to survive a lethal strike.

name: Ursamajor
description: Visited Earth on a cruise, but strayed from the tour group and got left behind. Works at NASA hoping to sneak onboard a rocket. Gets stronger the more damage he takes.

name: Nimoy Bore
description: His bowl cut helps contain the force of his rational power. Looking for a dashing starship captain to help him learn how to feel. Clears the way with logic and tusks.
special_ability: 50% chance to knockback all Cat Units.

name: Elizabeth the LVIth
description: Scion of the cyber-pigpen, Liz almost ended her line after choking on a mushroom. She's still blue to this day. Uses powerful wave attacks.
special_ability: 100% chance to create a Lv.3 Shockwave.

name: Galactic Overseer Nyandam (Alien)
description: Has the nightmarish power to redirect all your future email to a random address. You'll never know why all your friends forgot about you. Attacks sometimes slow movement.
special_ability: 50% chance to slow all Cat Units for 120f 4 seconds.

name: Scissoroo
description: Former welterweight champ of Gliese 832c. Stripped of her title once judges noticed the custom gloves she wore in round 4. They really help deliver powerful knockback.
special_ability: 30% chance to knockback all Cat Units.

name: Cyberhorn (Alien)
description: A killing machine tasked with one purpose: stop Cat pictures from being posted to the internet. Meant to join for Chapter 1, but he was too slow to catch the bus.

name: Mistress Celeboodle (Alien)
description: Only daughter of the most powerful political dynasty of Centauri year 1192. Beauty, brains, wit... and yet she married a chihuahua reality TV "star". Gets stronger after being damaged.
special_ability: Attack power will increase 100% at 75% health

name: Alpacky
description: Camelle super-glued cotton balls to herself to become an Alpaca. Allergic to the fibers, so she can't stop coughing and spitting, but she's too proud to admit when she's wrong.

name: Elder Sloth
description: THE SLOTH's grandpa bought a lifetime pass to a hot spring resort. Healing minerals in the water he spends all his time in have given him super speed and powerful knockback abilities!

name: Gorilliam
special_ability: 50% chance to warp Cat Units back by 500 range for 10f 0.33 seconds.

name: Satan Claus
special_ability: 100% chance to warp Cat Units back 750 range for 40f 1.33 seconds.

name: Puffley's Comet
description: An aspiring idol that appears once every 100 years, long mistaken for an asteroid. His entourage of loyal fans form a shining tail that can be seen from light-years away.
special_ability:
100% chance to knockback all Cat Units;
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -500~500).

name: Super Hyppoh
special_ability:
100% chance to slow all Cat Units for 60f 2 seconds;
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -300~350).

name: Shibalien Elite (Alien)
description: Officer-class Doge in the Alien Marines. Received top marks in the academy specializing in Warp attacks. But the job market is tough these days.
special_ability: 35% chance to warp Cat Units back by 750 range for 10f 0.33 seconds.

name: Star Peng (Alien)
description: The originator of Warp-field tactics. The Peng people are a proud warrior race with advanced scientific knowledge, thanks to a culture of daily sudoku.
special_ability: 100% chance to warp Cat Units back by 500 range for 100f 3.33 seconds.

name: General GreGory (Alien)
description: A mighty tactician who's still single thanks to his scary face. He is actually an excellent cook and has a six-octave vocal range, but he is too shy to show anyone his talents.

name: Le'Solar (Alien)
description: The mother of all Le'Boins, she will protect her sweet children with her iron hide. Invades at least new three planets a week to maintain her lovely curves.

name: Project A (Alien)
description: He can sense all your dirty thoughts. Keep your mind pure around him, or the lewd energies will make him stronger. Has no real experience whatsoever.
special_ability: 20% chance to warp Cat Units back by 500 range for 10f (0.33 seconds).

name: Corporal Weyland (Alien)
description: A proud soldier of the great Mole Army, safeguarding peace and love throughout the cosmos. His antimatter uppercut catapults Cats to another dimension.

name: UltraBaaBaa
description: Stellar sheep with mighty barrier defense. Spiky looks are actually just bad bedhead. Since everyone keeps their distance, she's paranoid about her breath.

name: Kid Tappa
description: Express delivery across the galaxy! His girlfriend thinks he should start looking for a real job, so he's joined the elite Alien shock division.

name: Ribbo (Alien)
description: Underrated genius chef at a starred eatery. He warps anything that looks unappealing back to the kitchen. What's the best wine to pair with Cat?

name: Mesocosmocyclone (Alien)
description: Rumored to be the  secret lovechild of a famous storm. It’s impossible to guess who it is, though. Warps anyone who comes close. Low stamina, so try going all-out!
special_ability: 100% chance to warp Cat Units forward by 150 range for 100f 3.33 seconds.

name: Gardeneel Bros. (Alien)
description: This mean gang of fishy bad boys have had it with the Cats causing trouble in their territory. Out of the dirt and ready to fight! Don’t call them snakes, they don’t like that.
special_ability:
Long Distance (Effective range: 1,700~1,950);
Teleports Cat Units forward by 1375 range for 1f (100%)

name: Axoloty
description: A space salamander with a Cat allergy. The powerful winds of its relentless sneezes are [sic] should be avoided by small Cats who could be blown into another dimension.

name: Super Cosmic Cyclone
description: A tear in space time that opened up inside a nebula. Manipulates the continuum to warp Cats away. Victory is possible if you attack it from long-distance.
special_ability: 100% chance to warp Cat Units back by 500 range for 1f 0.03 seconds.

name: Everlord Wanwan
description:
Universe's #1 playboy, beloved by
lonely-heart madames from across the 
galaxy. Just a few sweet words from him
and anyone will soon be seeing stars.
special_ability:
Multi-hit attacks (15,000 at 39f, 15,000 at 69f, 1,500 at 89f)
Warps Cat Units back 2000 range for 2000f on last hit (100%)
Omni Strike (Effective range: -500~1000)

name: Metal Hippoe
description: A certain organization decided to experiment and make Hippoe's body metal. Appears to be weak to critical attacks.

name: Super Metal Hippoe
description: Metal Hippoe who abused file sharing software and came down with the Trojan virus, now he's out of control. Appears to be weak to critical attacks.
special_ability: 100% chance to knockback all Cat Units.

name: Metal One Horn (Metal)
description: A One Horn who underwent cybernetic enhancement. He can intercept radio waves and dispatches almost instantly. Still never makes it in time.

name: Teacher Cybear
description: Teacher Bear received experimental cybernetic implants for more powerful, efficient education. His lessons are now too intense for children and he had to find work at a trade college.

name: CyberFace (Metal)
description: A relic of humanity's final war, this cyborg crushes all to dust with enhanced jaw strength. Seems to float, but actually scampers around on a dozen plasma legs invisible to the eye.

name: Sir Metal Seal
description:
A seal who traveled to the city,
dreaming of superstardom.
Wanted more attention so
he decided to go full cyborg.

name: Angel Fanboy
description: Blew his life savings on Angel goods. Discovered Angels aren't actually Floating enemies after obsessively collecting Rare Cat Capsules.

name: Metal Doge
description:
Walking home from prep school,
a giant silver disc appeared in the sky.
Can't remember what happened next, but
now he wears only silver jumpsuits?

name: Croconator
description:
Croco volunteered for cyborgization to
become the most powerful member of
his clan. They ran out of budget partway
though, but he makes the look work.

name: Koronium
description: Mascot/base coach for the NLB Champions, Koala Krushers. Forced replays of several games by interfering when his team is losing. His harshness during training is feared by all.

name: Angry Sun
special_ability:
100% chance to freeze all Cat Units for 60f 2 seconds;
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow and Weaken.

name: Metal Cyclone
description: Attacks continuously while moving so no one can stop its cyclonic force. A maelstrom of flying metal shards. Its heavy body keeps it from floating.

name: Zoge (Zombie)
description: Doge's late father, buried several years ago. Even the grave couldn't stop him from worrying over his kids' grades. Only showing a report card can put him permanently to rest.
special_ability:
100% chance to burrow underground 500 when a Cat enters its range (1 time);
100% chance to revive at 50% HP after being dead for 240f 8 seconds (1 time).

name: Znache (Zombie)
description: A slithery creature who uses watercolors for horror makeup (really already dead, though.) The only information you need is that it possesses gruesome area attack powers.
special_ability:
100% chance to burrow underground 1,500 after a Cat enters its range (1 time);
100% chance to revive at 50% HP after being dead for 180f 6 seconds (1 time).

name: Zomboe
description: Wandered through a poison bog one gloomy night and later woke up dead. (S)he doesn't seem to mind though. Now we'll never know if it's a he or she.

name: Zigge
description: Even death can't make this royal swine give up the throne. Wears a stylish skull until her stolen crown can be reclaimed. "I don't rot, I just age like fine wine."

name: Zackie Peng
description: After his debut film bombed, a big hole was all that's left where Peng's heart used to be. Even death by bad reviews won't stop his revenge on ungrateful audiences!
special_ability:
100% chance to revive at 50% HP after knocked down for 180f 6 seconds (1 time);
100% chance to burrow underground 1,125 when a Cat enters its range (1 time).

name: Zory
description: After being rejected from Heaven thanks to his scary face, Gory now wanders the earth. Someone tore off the top of his head while he gambled, thinking it was a toupee. Ouch.
special_ability:
100% chance to revive at 100% HP after being killed for 360f 12 seconds (1 time);
100% chance to burrow underground 625 when a Cat enters its range (1 time).

name: Zir Zeal (Zombie)
description: Through the morning mists, I beheld a Seal. He called me to join him in a voice neither living nor dead, beckoning me to join him on the distant shore of an uncanny world...

name: Zang Roo (Zombie)
description: After 50 years as a boxer, her body just couldn't handle the doping anymore. Still, chemicals were effective enough to keep her body punching even after death.

name: Zroco (Zombie)
description:
A poor gator who died of hunger.
Too weak to swim across the River Styx, it came back to this world as a half-baked ghost. Sometimes mistaken for dumbells.

name: Lord Gravey (Zombie)
description: Some squatter has made his home in Zoge's grave! How rude! Whoever this mysterious cadaver is, his will to rock seems to be alive and well.
special_ability:
- Knock back all Cat Units (100%)
- Revives at 100% HP after knocked down 120f (1 time)

name: Miss Haka (Zombie)
description: Zoge's wife was supposed to be buried here, but she's still alive at 158 and it seems like someone else took over the open real estate.
special_ability:
Burrows for 500f when a Cat enters it range (infinitely);
Revives at 100% HP after being knocked out 240f (1 time)

name: Big Sal
description: Best leave this lazybones be, he'll chomp anyone who disturbs his naptime. Or worse: he'll tell you neverending stories about his minor league baseball career.
special_ability:
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base)
Burrows underground 250 when a Cat enters its range (Unlimited)
Revives at 50% HP after being dead for 120f (1 time)

name: Coffin Zoge (Zombie)
description: An ancient hero of the Doge Army. Registered last year as an endangered species... the elder dead live a lonely life. Scholarly name: Canis Deadus Doornailus
special_ability: 100% chance to revive at 100% HP after being dead for 60f 2 seconds (unlimited).

name: Zamelle (Zombie)
description: Passed away after botched plastic surgery on her unfashionable hump. Makes for a beautiful corpse - the first undead cover girl! Don't mention the unnatural fur tone...
special_ability:
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base)
Revives at 100% HP after being dead for 240f (unlimited)

name: Cadaver Bear
description: Made up of the strongest parts from several expired Teacher Bears. The head wouldn't sit right, so it had to be bolted on. Urge to kill seems to be growing...
special_ability:
100% chance to burrow underground for 1,125 after a Cat enters its range (1 time);
100% chance to revive at 100% HP after being dead for 360f 12 seconds (1 time).

name: Dread Bore
description: Thanks to a tragic accident with a perm machine, this piggy both gained a stylish set of dreadlocks... and became an ex-Bore. Talk about a sudden image change.
special_ability:
Burrows underground for 1125f after a Cat enters its range (1 time)
Revives at 50% HP after being dead for 150f (1 time)

name: Zuche
description: A mad scientist set his tail on fire to test the limits of fowl power. Panic has given him the strength he needs to fly to heaven.

name: The Thrillerz
description: The guys are never alone in life or in death. Luckily there was a shuttle bus service from the cemetary to the battlefield. Undeath doesn't cure codependency...
special_ability:
100% chance to burrow underground 500 after a Cat enters its range (2 times);
100% chance to revive at 100% HP after being dead for 240f 8 seconds (1 time).

name: Li'l Zyclone
description:
Beloved nephew of childless uncle Zyclone.
Has his mother's toughness and father's timid
spirit, combining them into a hungry little storm
who hides at the first sign of danger.
special_ability:
Burrows underground 1,250 after a Cat enters its range (1 time)
Revives with 100% HP after being dead for 120f (4 seconds) (1 time)

name: Zollow
description: A bird so ripped that it can swim across the River Styx whenever it wants to. Upset that he can't stop the the mass he worked so hard to cultivate from rotting away.

name: Zyclone (Zombie)
description: The spirits of those defeated by the Battle Cats have gathered into a vengeful storm. How can you defeat a whirlwind that is already dead?
special_ability: Revives with 100% HP after being defeated for 120f (∞ times)

name: Daboo of the Dead
description: "The best zombie is an educated zombie," is what Poppa always said. It's just back issues of trashy horror comics inside that ominous cover, though. Immune to all negative effects.

name: Dead Donny Dash
Death Angel Z-Onel
description:
Clionel-type being who somehow survived(?)
the mass extinction of their world's polluted
oceans. Don't come near me or my sons ever
again. Said to paralyze Cats with fright.

name: Inumusha
description: A Doge warrior spirit possessed an up-and-coming young actor who took on his role in a stage adaptation of his legend. Don't get too close... his cursed castle might just react too.

name: Relic Bun-Bun
description: An unstoppable artifact who mercilessly crushes any intruder into the realm of the ancients. The prophecies speak of some who can resist the dark curses this guardian places on its foes.
special_ability:
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -300~300);
100% chance to curse Cat Units for 300f 10 seconds.

name: Relic Doge
description: Ancestral nemesis of the Cat Empire. Serious and hardworking like any Doge, but sometimes thoughtlessly lets a Curse out when focusing hard. Oops, sorry about that!
special_ability: 35% chance to curse all Cat Units for 100f 3.33 seconds.

name: Sir Rel
description: Speaks only in Olde English, meaning he's a very young Relic. If the Cats took their studies seriously, they might learn a lot from this guy.
special_ability: 100% chance to curse Cat Units for 150f 5 seconds.

name: Oldhorn
description: An ancient prophet who learns of impending doom by time-traveling. His time-trips aren't very accurate, so by the time he gets home the bad stuff has already happened.
special_ability: 100% chance to curse Cat Units for 300f 10 seconds.

name: Loris (Relic)
description: Last year's in-vogue celebrity, famous for his flashy taste in eyewear. But it's actually just what his eyes look like... Weird how he can throw them like that. Relics, amirite?
special_ability:
Long Distance (Effective Range: 500~800);
100% chance to curse Cat Units for 150f (5 seconds).

name: M. Ost (Relic)
description: Ostrich who is also a veteran stand-up comic. An inspiration for younger comedians, but he is becoming more self-conscious of the generation gap in the scene.

name: Mr. Puffington (Relic)
description: Branch manager of an undersea trading company. Once known for his poisonous personality, marriage has made him more approachable in spite of his prickly looks.
special_ability:
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -350~350);
100% chance to curse Cat Units for 300f 10 seconds.

name: Primeval Cyclone
description:
The most ancient of cyclones, born from
the Big Bang itself. Hasn't weakened even
after devouring the dinosaurs. Inflicts Curse,
grows stronger after taking damage.
special_ability:
Strengthens by 200% at 50% health;
100% chance to curse all Cat Units for 450f 15 seconds.

name: Evil Emperor Cat
description: The promised lord of Cats, consumed bypride in his mastery of elder forest sorceries.Now the king of ruin, he lashes out at thisdecadent world with furious Surges and Curses.

name: Dogumaru (Relic)
description: An ancient fighter excavated by the Doges. Clay body looks weak but is reinforced with Relic power. His human top was mistakenly attached to a horse body, but it still works(?)
special_ability:
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -500~700);
100% chance to curse Cat Units for 600f 20 seconds.

name: Urs & Fenrir
description:
Guardians of the primeval wilderness.
No intruder into their sacred forest has
ever walked out alive. Only those who
defeat them can peek behind the mask.
special_ability:
Reduces attack power of all Cat Units to 10% for 120f (4 seconds) (100%)
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -500~500)
Curses Cat Units for 120f (4 seconds) (100%)

name: Idi:Re
description:
Subject 002 (Paleobacterial Lifeform)
Combat Potential: Immeasurable.
Despite appearance, Floating trait not present
Output corresponds to weakened capacity

name: Relic Doge Base
special_ability:
100% chance to curse all Cat Units for 300f 10 seconds;
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow and Weaken.

name: Corrupted Cat Base
special_ability:
Creates a Lv.20 Shockwave (100%)
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow, Weaken and Surges

name: Walpurgisnacht
special_ability:
Slows down Cat Units for 75f (100%)
Critical Hit (100%)
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base)
Omni Strike (Effective range: -2000~1500)
Resist Waves, Knockback, Weaken, Freeze and Slow

name: Homulilly
special_ability:
Knocks back Cat Units (100%)
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base)
Lowers the attack power of all Cat Units to 50% for 150f (100%)
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -1800~1800)
Resist Waves, Knockback, Weaken, Slow and Freeze

name: Ramiel
special_ability:
Base Destroyer (deals x4 damage to Cat Base);
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -2500~2000).

name: Bardiel
special_ability:
Long Distance (Effective Range: 200~750);
Reduces attack power of all cats to 50% for 150f (100%).

name: Zeruel
special_ability:
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -3600~900)
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow and Weaken

name: Awakened Eva Unit-13
special_ability:
Knocks back all Cat Units (100%)
Freezes all Cat Units for 150f (100%)
Lowers the attack power of Cat Units to 50% for 750f (100%)
Attack power increases by 100% at 50% health
Omni Strike (Effective Range: -3600~1200)
Immune to Waves, Knockback, Freeze, Slow and Weaken
